<h4>Create an account on WeDeploy</h4>
<p>Now go and <a href="#">create a WeDeploy account</a>, if you don't have one already.</p>
<h4>Create a new project</h4>
<p>On the <a href="https://console.wedeploy.com/projects">WeDeploy Console</a>, create a new project (name it whatever you want üëç).</p>
<h4>Link your GitHub account</h4>
<p>Inside of your new project on the Console:</p>
<ol>
<li>Go to <em>Deployment</em></li>
<li>Select <em>GitHub</em></li>
<li>Go to <em>Connect to GitHub</em></li>
<li>Select <em>Authorize application</em></li>
</ol>
